data.title: Devilman Crybaby Anime's Special Movie Features Classic Opening Theme
data.meta_description: Here's the special movie for Netflix's upcoming Devilman Crybaby anime, w/c features the classic Devilman theme song.
data.text:
The official Devilman Crybaby anime website streamed the a new "special movie" of the upcoming anime. The video features the show's opening theme "Devilman no Uta" by Avu-chan, who will also voice Devil King Zenon in the show.

In addition, Denki Groove will also perform the show's theme song "MAN HUMAN" while Takkyuu to Tabibito will perform the special ending theme song "Konya Dake" for the show's 9th episode.
